msgstr "Bantuan"

#: app/templates/help.html:7
msgid ""
"Grylli includes built-in instructions throughout the app to help you "
"configure and manage your setup."
msgstr ""
"Grylli termasuk arahan terbina dalam sepanjang aplikasi untuk membantu anda "
"mengkonfigurasi dan menguruskan tetapan anda."

#: app/templates/help.html:8
msgid ""
"This page provides an overview of key features and direct links to where "
"they can be managed."
msgstr ""
"Halaman ini menyediakan gambaran keseluruhan ciri utama dan pautan langsung "
"ke tempat di mana ia boleh diuruskan."

