msgid "Security"
msgstr "🔐 Keselamatan"

#: app/templates/help.html:39
msgid "Grylli encrypts sensitive data and logs all key actions for auditing."
msgstr ""
"Grylli menyulitkan data sensitif dan merekod semua tindakan utama untuk "
